com.percussion.pso.utils
Class PSOSlotContents

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.pso.utils.PSOSlotContents

public class PSOSlotContents
extends Object

Tool for loading the contents of a slot as PSAaRelationship objects. The standard load method in Web Services IPSContentWs.loadContentRelations(PSRelationshipFilter, boolean) loads all content relationships, regardless of slot. This tool uses this method and returns a filtered and sorted list of PSAaRelationship objects.

Note that this tool is based on relationships and does not work on autoslots. If you are assembling a item, consider using PSOSlotTools.getSlotContents(com.percussion.services.assembly.IPSAssemblyItem, String, java.util.Map) instead of this method.

The returned slot has not been filtered by any item filters, and the revisions of the dependent items will not have been set.

The implementation of this method is highly dependent on the sortrank property of the relationships having been set correctly. The behavior when the sortrank is missing or invalid (e.g. 0 or -1) may be inconsistent.

Author:
DavidBenua
